getPrices((address,address,address,uint8.details: this method will return estimations for swap for one base token it can not be view, but to get estimation you have to call it in a static way Tokens that do not have `.decimals()` are not supported

params._data: array of PriceData, each PriceData can accept multiple pools per one price, price is fetched from pool, that has biggest liquidity (quote.balanceOf(pool))

returns.prices: prices normalized from input amount (10 ** prices[n].amountInDecimals) to one token price
